SAMPLE SIZE: 
______ 
The initial target sample size is ​377 participants​. If a statistically significant effect is not 
observed after the first round of data collection, a second round will begin. The second round of 
data collection will sample an additional ​187 participants​ for a pooled sample of ​564 
participants. ​In order to reach the stage 1 analytic sample size of 377, we will recruit 500 
participants to account for attrition. If a second stage is needed, we will recruit 248 additional 
participants, to reach the stage 2 analytic sample size of 187 additional participants  
 
14.
